title: Cosmic Caverns
content:
Here it is, the one Cosmo site that'll stay active as long as I'm active.

[url=http://spatang.com/cosmo/]spatang.com/cosmo/[/url]The unknown future rolls towards us. I face it for the first time with a sense of hope. Because if a machine, a Terminator, can learn the value of human life, maybe we can too.
